{
  "id": "69ae8572c0a3acffdc6c50cd",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:ブロック図のこと",
  "created": 1773045131,
  "updated": 1773055611,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ae8572c0a3acffdc6c50cd",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:ブロック図のこと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045131,
      "updated": 1773045131
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858a00000000004152a5",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045131,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152a6",
      "text": "はいはーい！今日のゆるトークのテーマは「ブロック図」だよ～。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152a7",
      "text": "ぶっちゃけさ、名前だけ聞くと「ブロックで図つくるん？」って感じなんだけどｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152a8",
      "text": "りか先生、このへんどうなん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152aa",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ab",
      "text": "ブロック図は、システムの構造や処理の流れを「箱（ブロック）」と「矢印」で表現する図。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ac",
      "text": "複雑な仕組みを抽象化して理解しやすくするための表現方法だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ad",
      "text": "たとえば、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ae",
      "text": ">入力 → 処理 → 出力",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152af",
      "text": "この三つを箱にしてつなぐだけでも、立派なブロック図になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152b0",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152b1",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Block_diagram",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152b3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152b4",
      "text": "あー！それなら見たことあるかも！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152b5",
      "text": "なんか理科の授業とかで「センサー → コンピュータ → モーター」みたいなやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152b6",
      "text": "要するにさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152b7",
      "text": ">「何が入ってきて → どう処理して → 何が出るか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152b8",
      "text": "っていう流れを、箱でざっくり見せるやつって感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ba",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152bb",
      "text": "その理解で正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152bc",
      "text": "ポイントは三つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152bd",
      "text": " 1. 細かい中身は省略する（抽象化）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152be",
      "text": " 2. 機能ごとに箱で分ける（モジュール化）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152bf",
      "text": " 3. 矢印で関係や流れを示す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152c0",
      "text": "プログラム設計、電子回路、システム設計など、いろんな分野で使われる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152c2",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152c3",
      "text": "まあ……それはまるで、物語の筋書きのようですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152c4",
      "text": "登場人物がそれぞれの役割を持ち、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152c5",
      "text": "ひとつの出来事から次の出来事へと物語が流れていく……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152c6",
      "text": "その流れを、箱と矢印で静かに並べたものが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152c7",
      "text": "ブロック図なのかもしれませんね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152c8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152c9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ca",
      "text": "おお～文学的ぃ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152cb",
      "text": "つまりさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152cc",
      "text": " 箱＝キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152cd",
      "text": " 矢印＝ストーリーの流れ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ce",
      "text": "って思うとわかりやすいかも！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152d0",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152d1",
      "text": "完全な比喩ではないが、理解の助けにはなる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152d2",
      "text": "ただし、ブロック図の重要な役割は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152d3",
      "text": "複雑なシステムを俯瞰することだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152d4",
      "text": "詳細な設計図ではなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152d5",
      "text": "「全体構造」を把握するためのマップ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152d6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152d7",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152d8",
      "text": "なるほど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152d9",
      "text": "森の中を歩くとき、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152da",
      "text": "一本一本の木を見つめるだけでは道を見失いますものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152db",
      "text": "高い丘に登り、森全体の姿を眺める。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152dc",
      "text": "ブロック図とは、その丘のようなものなのでしょう。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152de",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152df",
      "text": "うわ、それエモい例え。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152e0",
      "text": "でも確かにさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152e1",
      "text": "プログラムとか機械ってめちゃくちゃ複雑じゃん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152e2",
      "text": "いきなり細かい説明されると",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152e3",
      "text": "[**** 「情報量バグってて草」]ってなるんだよねｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152e5",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152e6",
      "text": "その問題を避けるために、エンジニアは段階的に設計する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152e7",
      "text": " 1. ブロック図（全体構造）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152e8",
      "text": " 2. サブブロック図（各部分）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152e9",
      "text": " 3. 詳細設計",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ea",
      "text": "トップダウン設計の基本だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152eb",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ec",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Top-down_and_bottom-up_design",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ee",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ef",
      "text": "まあ……まるで、長い小説を書くときの構成のようですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152f0",
      "text": "まずは大まかな章立てを作り、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152f1",
      "text": "それから一つ一つの場面を描いていく……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152f2",
      "text": "人の考える営みというものは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152f3",
      "text": "分野が違っても、どこか似通うものなのですね。（笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152f4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152f5",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152f6",
      "text": "あ、でもさ質問！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152f7",
      "text": "ブロック図ってさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152f8",
      "text": "フローチャートと何が違うの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152f9",
      "text": "どっちも矢印あるし、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152fa",
      "text": "正直ちょっとごっちゃになるんだけどｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152fc",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152fd",
      "text": "良い質問。違いは目的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152fe",
      "text": " ブロック図",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c00000000004152ff",
      "text": "  → システムの「構造」を表す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415300",
      "text": " フローチャート",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415301",
      "text": "  → 処理の「手順」を表す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415302",
      "text": "例：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415303",
      "text": "ブロック図",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415304",
      "text": " code:block.mermaid",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415305",
      "text": "  graph TD",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415306",
      "text": "  A[センサ] --> B[制御装置] --> C[モーター]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415307",
      "text": " フローチャート",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415308",
      "text": " code:code:flowchart.mermaid",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773046858
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415309",
      "text": "  graph TD",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041530a",
      "text": "  A((開始)) --> B[センサーを読む]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041530b",
      "text": "  B -->C{値が大きい？}",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041530c",
      "text": "  C -->|Yes|D[モーターON]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041530d",
      "text": "  C -->|No|E[モーターOFF]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041530e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041530f",
      "text": "前者は構造。後者はアルゴリズム。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415310",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415311",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415312",
      "text": "あー！わかった！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415313",
      "text": " ブロック図＝地図",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415314",
      "text": " フローチャート＝レシピ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415315",
      "text": "みたいな感じか！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415316",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415317",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415318",
      "text": "とても素敵なたとえですね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415319",
      "text": "地図があれば、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041531a",
      "text": "私たちはどこへ向かうのかを知ることができる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041531b",
      "text": "そしてレシピがあれば、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041531c",
      "text": "どのように進めばよいかがわかる……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041531d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041531e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041531f",
      "text": "その二つを組み合わせると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415320",
      "text": "システム設計はかなり理解しやすくなる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415321",
      "text": "エンジニアリングでは基本スキル。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415322",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415323",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415324",
      "text": "なるほどね～。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415325",
      "text": "今日のまとめいくよ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415326",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415327",
      "text": "[** ブロック図まとめ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415328",
      "text": " 箱と矢印でシステムをざっくり表す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415329",
      "text": " 細かい中身は省略してOK",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041532a",
      "text": " 全体の構造を理解するための図",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041532b",
      "text": " フローチャートとは目的が違う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041532c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041532d",
      "text": "って感じ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041532e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041532f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415330",
      "text": "ええ、とてもよく整理されていますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415331",
      "text": "目には見えない仕組みを、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415332",
      "text": "形あるものとして描き出す……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415333",
      "text": "ブロック図とは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415334",
      "text": "思考をそっと紙の上に咲かせる花のようなものなのかもしれませんね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415335",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415336",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415337",
      "text": "……詩的すぎるが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415338",
      "text": "概念可視化ツールという点では間違っていない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415339",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041533a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041533b",
      "text": "りか、ちょっとツンで草ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041533c",
      "text": "じゃあ次回はさ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041533d",
      "text": "「フローチャート」をもっと深掘りしてみる？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773055586
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041533e",
      "text": "ゲームのAIとか作るときにも使うし、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c000000000041533f",
      "text": "絶対ネタ多いと思うんだよね～！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae858c0000000000415340",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773045132,
      "updated": 1773045132
    },
    {
      "id": "69aeae6b0000000000496bbd",
      "text": "[ゆるトーク:フローチャートこと]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773055596,
      "updated": 1773055611
    },
    {
      "id": "69aeae750000000000496bbf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773055606,
      "updated": 1773055606
    }
  ]
}